801
00:48:14,120 --> 00:48:16,360
Then you have Aeschylus,
Sophrates, and Eupodes.

802
00:48:16,360 --> 00:48:18,380
And what they did that was different is,

803
00:48:18,620 --> 00:48:22,400
rather than think
directly at the audience,

804
00:48:22,680 --> 00:48:26,200
they had the characters face each
other in a dialogue, in a debate.

805
00:48:27,360 --> 00:48:30,400
Okay? And by doing this,

806
00:48:30,560 --> 00:48:34,240
what happens is you

807
00:48:34,240 --> 00:48:38,640
create the capacity for perspective

808
00:48:38,640 --> 00:48:40,720
and inner debate.

809
00:48:41,340 --> 00:48:45,400
Right? Because before, you were part of...

810
00:48:46,900 --> 00:48:48,180
the story.

811
00:48:48,420 --> 00:48:52,140
Now you have to step
