825
00:49:39,080 --> 00:49:43,900
You are no longer influenced by the
crowd or the emotions of the actor.

826
00:49:44,440 --> 00:49:45,760
You can just look at the words themselves.

827
00:49:46,360 --> 00:49:47,920
And judge them on their own merit.

828
00:49:48,360 --> 00:49:51,960
You also have the capacity now to reflect.

829
00:49:52,180 --> 00:49:56,040
Meaning, you can go back to the words
