830
00:49:56,440 --> 00:50:00,040
To constantly reflect on
their meaning and logic.

831
00:50:00,200 --> 00:50:01,800
Okay? You understand?

832
00:50:02,100 --> 00:50:03,540
So, when you add these
three things together.

833
00:50:04,060 --> 00:50:06,520
Homer created the capacity
for empathy and imagination.

834
00:50:07,140 --> 00:50:11,020
The playwright created the capacity
for inner debate and perspective.

835
00:50:11,780 --> 00:50:15,460
The philosophers created the
capacity for reason and reflection.

836
00:50:16,360 --> 00:50:19,220
You now have a new human mind.

837
00:50:19,540 --> 00:50:24,100
Okay? And when you study all of them.

